[b][font=Arial]____________________________

Installation:

- Download the File and place it at:
"Steam\SteamApps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets"
- Open Skyrim with SKSE.
- Load any workin save file.
- Open the console usin the "^" button.
- Type "showracemenu"
- Select Nord Race"
- Look for the slide option: "Preset Slot"
- Select the Slot "50" and press "F9", this should load the Character Face.
- Customize your Character as you like.
